}}'''皮匠山'''（{{lang-en|The Cobbler}}，[[苏格兰盖尔语|苏格兰盖尔语]]：Beinn Artair）是一座海拔為884米（2900英尺）的山，位于[[蘇格蘭|苏格兰]]{{link-en|长湖 (蘇格蘭)|Loch Long|长湖}}附近。该山是{{link-en|阿罗卡尔阿尔卑斯山|Arrochar Alps}}的一部分。該山因其巨大的山顶岩石類似一个鞋匠在弯腰，故得名皮匠山。皮匠山是[[攀岩|攀岩]]愛好者常光顧地點<ref name="Townsend">{{cite book |author=Chris Townsend |year=2011 |title=Scotland |publisher=[[Cicerone_Press|Cicerone Press]] |isbn=9781852844424 |chapter=The Cobbler |pages=106–107 |chapter-url=https://books.google.com/books?id=yoVZWInM98cC&pg=PA106 |access-date=2020-08-21 |archive-date=2020-08-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200802083135/https://books.google.com/books?id=yoVZWInM98cC&pg=PA106 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

